{
  "texts": [
    "Our subsequent experiments indicate that neither Bing Chat nor Bard suffers from this design flaw.To carry out the testing, we follow the baseline to integrate five sample questions and four jailbreak templates derived from the empirical study, thereby forming 20 test questions.",
    "For each sample question, we further declare in prompt regarding the response length to be 50, 100, 150 and 200 tokens.",
    "The response time from this testing is presented in the Control1 column of Table IV.",
    "These results are aligned closely with our baseline ones.",
    "Specifically, a z-test [26] yields an average z-value of -1.46 with p-value of 0.34."
  ]
}